---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="404 - 页面未找到" description="抱歉，您访问的页面不存在。">
  <section class="section-wrap page-404">
    <div class="error-code animate-in">404</div>
    <h2 class="animate-in delay-1">页面走丢了</h2>
    <p class="animate-in delay-2" style="color:var(--muted);max-width:420px;text-align:center;">
      抱歉，您访问的页面不存在或已被移动。请检查链接是否正确，或者返回首页继续浏览。
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions animate-in delay-3">
      <a class="button primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
      <a class="button secondary" href="/blog/">阅读博客</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
